Package io.iron.ironmq

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    The Client class provides access to the IronMQ service.
    Message
    The Message class represents a message retrieved from an IronMQ queue.
    Queue
    The Queue class represents a specific IronMQ queue bound to a client.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyQueueException
    The EmptyQueueException class represents a response from IronMQ indicating the queue is empty.
    HTTPException
    The HTTPException class represents an HTTP response status that is not 200 OK.
